name: Max Abstractions
body:
### Max MSP Abstractions
These are all of my Max/MSP abstractions.  They are small patches with singular functions that I use over again.

### Abstractions
* Panner
* Multi delays
* MIDI CC assigner
* sustainers

There are more to come as I get my patches more organized.
